                    <div class="post-user-info">
                        <img src="/themes/facebook/images/friend1.jpg" alt="Sarah Wilson" class="profile-pic">
                        <div>
                            <div class="post-user-name">Sarah Wilson</div>
                            <div class="post-time">2 hours ago · 🌍</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="post-menu">⋯</button>
                </div>
                <div class="post-content">
                    <div class="post-text">Just had an amazing day at the beach! The sunset was absolutely breathtaking. Sometimes you need to take a step back and appreciate the beautiful moments in life. 🌅✨

There's something magical about watching the sun dip below the horizon, painting the sky in brilliant oranges and pinks. The waves gently lapping at the shore, the warm sand beneath your feet, and the salty breeze in your hair - it's moments like these that remind me how beautiful our world truly is.

I spent hours just sitting there, watching the colors change and listening to the rhythm of the ocean. It's incredible how nature has this way of putting everything into perspective. All the stress and worries of daily life just seemed to melt away.

Feeling grateful for these peaceful moments and excited to share this beautiful view with all of you! ✨</div>
                    <img src="/themes/facebook/images/beach-sunset.jpg" alt="Beach sunset" class="post-image">
                </div>
                <div class="post-stats">
                    <span>👍❤️😊 245 people liked this</span>
                    <span>23 comments · 8 shares</span>
                </div>
